---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="About Silver | Pondering Silver" description="Learn more about Silver, the voice behind Pondering Silver, and the inner landscape that shapes each reflection.">
  <article class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-10">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-purple-700">
        About
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">About Silver</h1>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 sm:text-lg">
        I walk the line between deep introspection and a restless craving for adventure. Spirituality and self-discovery thread through everything I create here, guiding me through life&apos;s complexities and inspiring the offerings you&apos;ll find across this site.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
      <p>
        As a natural romantic at heart, I&apos;m always envisioning the next project or stage in life&apos;s unfolding story. The mundane doesn&apos;t hold my attention for long; I&apos;m driven by a desire for meaning and creativity that reaches beyond the ordinary.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a deep sensitivity to others and a powerful imagination, I thrive in the realms of human connection, intuition, and artistic expression. Music, symbolism, and the unconscious world captivate me, shaping how I approach relationships, growth, and spiritual practice.
      </p>
      <p>
        Balancing tangible realities with my internal visions is an ongoing practice. Life often feels like a grand theatre—one where I seek to live out the most vibrant, heartfelt, and meaningful stories.
      </p>
      <p>
        I value empathy and connection, yet I remain independent and unafraid to challenge conventions. Life is an adventure, and I&apos;m constantly in conversation with experiences that stretch me spiritually, emotionally, and creatively.
      </p>
      <p>
        Above all, I&apos;m committed to understanding myself and others—blending intuition with imagination to cultivate joy, depth, and wholeness.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Personality profile</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>Jungian Typology: INTP / Ti Ne</li>
        <li>Socionics: LII – 2 Ti</li>
        <li>Enneagram: 5 (Sexual subtype), 5w4 wing, Tritype 5sx – 9sx – 4sp</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
